# Design Standards

## Branding
- Title: Russell Jones
- Description: Crafting elegant solutions with modern web technologies

## Core Principles
- Follow accessibility standards (WCAG)
- Monitor performance metrics
- Use semantic HTML elements
- Validate user input
- Handle errors gracefully

